 Video Enhancement\n  - Improved the image quality of MR Videos and Artist Greetings, and also resolved occasional interruptions.\n  - For the T-Pain MR Concert, please delete the file and download it again to apply the improvements.\n3) Asset Improvements\n  - Fixed an issue where VFX occasionally did not render properly within the app.\n4) Storage Space Management Guide\n  - To ensure a smoother download experience for the VR Concert, it is recommended to have around 2GB more free space on your device than the file size indicated for the download.", "created_date": 1731476476, "id": "9144882705543582", "version": "2.1.154", "version_code": 34926, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "9144880732210446"}, "asset_files": {"count": 1}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6513803575318188", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9144882705543582"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1731388199, "id": "9137652926266560", "version": "2.1.153", "version_code": 34903, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": {"id": "9137641139601072"}, "asset_files": {"count": 1}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "6513803575318188", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "9144882705543582"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1728398767, "id": "8908701062495082", "version": "2.1.147", "v